          "text": [
            "<p><em>Drag the following text tile into your workspace to answer the questions.</em></p><p>Brainstorm at least three things your servo motor could be used for in real life. It could be something practical or entertaining.</p><ul><li>Idea 1:</li><li>Idea 2:</li><li>Idea 3:</li></ul><p>Now, choose one of your ideas and classroom materials to modify your physical servo.</p><p>Take a photo of your customized machine and upload it to your workspace in an image tile. Alternatively, you could make a detailed diagram using a drawing tile.</p>"
          ]
        }
